    "description": "<p>At 6th level, your body becomes infused with chaotic magic that makes harming you a dangerous proposition. When a creature you can see damages you, you can use your reaction to cast a spell of 1stor 2nd-level. The spell must either target the creature that damaged you or be centered on a space it occupies, it must have a casting time of 1 action or 1 bonus action, and you must spend sorcery points equal to the level of the spell in addition to the spell slot used.</p><p>At 14th and 18th level, the highest level of spell you can cast in this way increases by 1. </p>",
